5
00:01:38,881 --> 00:01:48,879
Next I use eggshells as fertilizer to stimulate flowering

6
00:01:57,877 --> 00:02:06,875
Crush about 5 eggshells

7
00:02:39,342 --> 00:02:49,367
Then add 50ml of vinegar water to help ferment and dissolve the organic calcium

8
00:02:56,066 --> 00:03:06,897
The reaction between vinegar water and eggshell creates organic calcium that dissolves very quickly

9
00:03:16,062 --> 00:03:26,060
Leave for 1 day to completely dissolve the calcium and minerals in the eggshell

10
