11
00:04:15,883 --> 00:04:23,882
Step 1: Water the roots every 2 weeks

12
00:04:30,315 --> 00:04:40,312
Eggshells contain a lot of calcium to help plants stay healthy and increase their resistance to pests

13
00:04:47,750 --> 00:04:57,742
